quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  25,1,Blessed (is) Who descended the Separator of Right and Wrong/Koran/Torah on (to) His worshipper/slave to be a warning/notice to the creations all together/(universes)
  25,2,"Who, for Him (is) the skies`/space`s and the earth`s/Planet Earth`s ownership and (He) did not take a child (son) , and a partner was not for Him in the ownership , and He created every thing so He predestined it predestination"
  25,3,"And they took from other than Him gods, they do not create a thing, and they are being created, and they do not own/possess to themselves harm, and nor benefit/usefulness , and they do not own/possess death/lifelessness, and nor life , and nor revival/resurrection"
  25,4,"And those who disbelieved say: \"That that (is) except lies/falsehood he fabricated/cut and split it, and a nation (of) others helped/assisted him on it.\" So they had come unjustly/oppressively and falsely"
  25,5,"And they said: \"The first`s/beginner`s myths/baseless stories , he wrote it, so it is being dictated on (to) him early mornings and evening to sunset"
  25,6,"Say: \"Who knows the secret in the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth descended it, that He truly is/was forgiving, merciful"
  25,7,"And they said: \"What to that (what is the matter) the messenger, he eats the food and walks in the markets, if only an angel was descended to him, so he (the angel) becomes a warner with him"
  25,8,"Or a treasure be thrown to him, or a treed garden/paradise be for him, he eats from it. And the unjust/oppressive said: \"That you follow except a bewitched/enchanted man"
  25,9,"See how they gave to you the examples/proverbs, so they were misguided, so they are not being able (of) a way/path"
  25,10,"Blessed (is) who, if He willed/wanted He made/created for you better than that, treed gardens/paradises, the rivers/waterways run/flow from below/beneath it, and He makes/puts for you castles/palaces"
  25,11,"But they denied with the Hour/Resurrection , and We prepared to who denied with the Hour/Resurrection blazing/inflaming (fire)"
  25,12,"If it saw them from a far/distant place/position , they heard/listened to it a rage/anger and (the) sound of roaring fire"
  25,13,"And if they were thrown from it (to) a narrow/tight place/position tied to each other, at that time and place they called (for) destruction and grief"
  25,14,"Do not call today (for) one destruction and grief , and call (for) many destruction(s) (and) grief(s)"
  25,15,"Say: \"Is that better or the immortality`s/eternity`s treed garden/paradise which was promised (to) the fearing and obeying, (it) was for them a reward and an end/destination"
  25,16,"For them in it what they will/want immortally/eternally, (it) was on your Lord a questioned promise"
  25,17,"And a day/time He gathers them and what they worship from other than God, so He says: \"Are you, you (who) misguided those My worshippers/slaves ? Or they misguided (from) the way/path"
  25,18,"They said: \"Your praise/glory (it) was, ought not (be) to us that we take from other than You from guardians/allies . And but you made them enjoy and their fathers, until they forgot the reminder, and they were a destroyed/failed nation"
  25,19,"So they had denied you because (of) what you say, so you do not be able (of) diversion and nor a victory/aid , and who causes injustice/oppresses from you, We make him taste/experience a great torture"
  25,20,"And We did not send from before you from the messengers except that they truly eat (E) the food and they walk in the markets, and We made/put some of you to some (as) a test/seduction , would you be patient? And your Lord was/is seeing/knowing"